If he has a real Intention to agree in caſe his Enterpriſe fails, the Diſcovery that will be made to him by Monſieur du Hallier, of his evil Projects, will not hinder him from proſecuting the good ones; 
                     Nothing hinders a Man from purſuing his Good, when he expects a good Succeſs by his Negotiations. You muſt be careful to diſcover whether the ſaid D. Charles has any Forces within ten Leagues of Nancy, which he might aſſemble on a ſudden. You muſt know where Monſicur de Ville is.
                   and if he makes no farther Inſtance about it, it will be a manifeſt Sign that he had nothing but Treaſon in his Mind.
